review:
A very typical 1st person shooter game which incorporate some modern military technology and scenarios. No difficulties settings or weapon choices, it's more about immersion than challenges. I quite enjoyed it, but it's not anything outstanding. 

My game also bugged mid way through mission 5, which means I didn't actually get to finish the game... game support didn't help much so I guess that's it for me on this game. 

Genre: 1st person FPS; chapter-based;
